name: AlignDistributeBounds
shortdesc: Options for aligning or distributing objects.

property.name: ITEM_BOUNDS
property.shortdesc: Align or distribute to the bounds of the objects.

property.name: PAGE_BOUNDS
property.shortdesc: Align or distribute to the bounds of the page.

property.name: MARGIN_BOUNDS
property.shortdesc: Align or distribute to the margins of the page.

property.name: SPREAD_BOUNDS
property.shortdesc: Align or distribute to the bounds of the spread.

property.name: KEY_OBJECT
property.shortdesc: Align or distribute to a key object.
